from uiflow import *

def fun_data_(topic_data):
# global params
label0.set_text(str(topic_data))
pass
label0.set_pos(0, 0)
m5mqtt = M5mqtt('yasuda', 'mqtt.uko.jp', 1883, 'icecream', 'UjSPfjxM', 300)

m5mqtt.start()
